Package com.safenetinc.luna.provider.keyfactory

JCA-compliant implementation of key factories that translate and create Luna keys for LunaProvider.

Package com.safenetinc.luna.provider.keyfactory Description

JCA-compliant implementation of key factories that translate and create Luna keys for LunaProvider. Only accessed from Luna provider framework. You should just refer to these classes for an idea of the provided mechanisms.
